

{"id":6743,"date":"2024-06-03T17:42:39","date_gmt":"2024-06-03T10:42:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/?p=6743"},"modified":"2024-06-04T09:27:27","modified_gmt":"2024-06-04T02:27:27","slug":"9-cach-tao-dong-luc-tap-luyen-cho-nguoi-moi-bat-dau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/9-cach-tao-dong-luc-tap-luyen-cho-nguoi-moi-bat-dau\/","title":{"rendered":"9 c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6751 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2207-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2207-1-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2207-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2207-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2207-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2207-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2207-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u00fang ta ai c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 9 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>1. Ch\u1ecdn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ng\u1eafn v\u00e0 t\u0103ng d\u1ea7n c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9. C\u00e1ch n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u00e1nh ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. H\u00e3y l\u1eafng nghe c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>2. X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chia nh\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>3.<\/b><b>T\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1edfng cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00e3y t\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1edfng cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n khi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eafm th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1eadp m\u1edbi khi b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c trong m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>4. Linh ho\u1ea1t thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n, h\u00e3y thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c tham gia c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi nh\u01b0 \u0111i b\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ea1p xe, b\u01a1i l\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn cho vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c lu\u00f4n m\u1edbi m\u1ebb v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>5. Lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u00e3y thay th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>6. Theo d\u00f5i qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng t\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m. S\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 t\u1eeb b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>7. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n b\u00e8<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>8. Trau d\u1ed3i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft th\u00eam v\u1ec1 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. H\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>9. T\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c b\u1eb1ng \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1o danh s\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t nh\u1ea1c y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 nghe khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Ho\u1eb7c m\u1edf danh s\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/open.spotify.com\/playlist\/7CfMhOX4NzAEuQgzFxXlwk?si=e4475d5bd4694530\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u201cFeel Good\u201d<\/a> tr\u00ean Spotify c\u1ee7a The New Gym. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The New Gym &#8211; Gym cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Email: cskh@thenewgym.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font